va:valueAssertion.test: if (not(matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^ISIN/.*')) and not(matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^CAU/.*'))) then (matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^CUSIP/[A-HJ-NP-Z0-9*@#]{8}\d$') or matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^SEDOL/[BCDF-HJ-NP-TV-Z0-9]{6}\d$') or matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^WKN/[A-Z0-9]{6}$') or matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^BT/.+') or matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^BBGID/BBG[BCDF-HJ-NP-TV-Z0-9]{8}\d$') or matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^RIC/.+') or matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^FIGI/[BCDF-HJ-NP-TV-Z]{2}G[BCDF-HJ-NP-TV-Z0-9]{8}\d$') or matches(string(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID), '^OCANNA/.+') or nilled(xfi:fact-typed-dimension-value($a,QName('http://eiopa.europa.eu/xbrl/s2c/dict/dim','UI'))/s2c_typ:ID)) else true()
